{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.1","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:1","prev_osis_id":"Matt.017.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le plus grand dans le royaume des cieux. \u2014 Les scandales<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-9: cf. (Mc 9:33-37. Lu 9:46-48.) Lu 22:24-27.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    En ce moment, les disciples s\u2019approch\u00e8rent de J\u00e9sus, et dirent: Qui donc est le plus grand dans le royaume des cieux?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.2","name":"Matthieu 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.17.27","name":"Matthieu 17:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.17.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.2","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:2","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>J\u00e9sus, ayant appel\u00e9 un petit enfant, le pla\u00e7a au milieu d\u2019eux,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.3","name":"Matthieu 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.1","name":"Matthieu 18:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.3","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:3","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>et dit: <span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">si vous ne vous convertissez et si vous ne devenez comme les petits enfants, vous n\u2019entrerez pas dans le royaume des cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.4","name":"Matthieu 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.2","name":"Matthieu 18:2","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.4","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:4","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi, quiconque se rendra humble comme ce petit enfant sera le plus grand dans le royaume des cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.5","name":"Matthieu 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.3","name":"Matthieu 18:3","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.5","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:5","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et quiconque re\u00e7oit en mon nom un petit enfant comme celui-ci, me re\u00e7oit moi-m\u00eame.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.6","name":"Matthieu 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.4","name":"Matthieu 18:4","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.6","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:6","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais, si quelqu\u2019un scandalisait un de ces petits qui croient en moi, il vaudrait mieux pour lui qu\u2019on suspend\u00eet \u00e0 son cou une meule de moulin, et qu\u2019on le jet\u00e2t au fond de la mer.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.7","name":"Matthieu 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.5","name":"Matthieu 18:5","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.7","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:7","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Malheur au monde \u00e0 cause des scandales!<\/span><span class=\"wj\">Car il est n\u00e9cessaire qu\u2019il arrive des scandales;<\/span><span class=\"wj\">mais malheur \u00e0 l\u2019homme par qui le scandale arrive!<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.8","name":"Matthieu 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.6","name":"Matthieu 18:6","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.8","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:8","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si ta main ou ton pied est pour toi une occasion de chute, coupe-les et jette-les loin de toi; mieux vaut pour toi entrer dans la vie boiteux ou manchot, que d\u2019avoir deux pieds ou deux mains et d\u2019\u00eatre jet\u00e9 dans le feu \u00e9ternel.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.9","name":"Matthieu 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.7","name":"Matthieu 18:7","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.9","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:9","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et si ton \u0153il est pour toi une occasion de chute, arrache-le et jette-le loin de toi; mieux vaut pour toi entrer dans la vie, n\u2019ayant qu\u2019un \u0153il, que d\u2019avoir deux yeux et d\u2019\u00eatre jet\u00e9 dans le feu de la g\u00e9henne.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.10","name":"Matthieu 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.8","name":"Matthieu 18:8","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.10","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:10","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.011,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La brebis \u00e9gar\u00e9e<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 10-14: cf. Lu 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Gardez-vous de m\u00e9priser un seul de ces petits; car je vous dis<\/span><span class=\"wj\">que leurs anges dans les cieux voient continuellement la face de mon P\u00e8re qui est dans les cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.11","name":"Matthieu 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.9","name":"Matthieu 18:9","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.11","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:11","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car le Fils de l\u2019homme est venu sauver ce qui \u00e9tait perdu.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.12","name":"Matthieu 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.10","name":"Matthieu 18:10","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.12","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:12","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Que vous en semble? Si un homme a cent brebis, et que l\u2019une d\u2019elles s\u2019\u00e9gare, ne laisse-t-il pas les quatre-vingt-dix-neuf autres sur les montagnes, pour aller chercher celle qui s\u2019est \u00e9gar\u00e9e?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.13","name":"Matthieu 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.11","name":"Matthieu 18:11","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.13","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:13","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et, s\u2019il la trouve, je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, elle lui cause plus de joie que les quatre-vingt-dix-neuf qui ne se sont pas \u00e9gar\u00e9es.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.14","name":"Matthieu 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.12","name":"Matthieu 18:12","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.14","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:14","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">De m\u00eame, ce n\u2019est pas la volont\u00e9 de votre P\u00e8re qui est dans les cieux qu\u2019il se perde un seul de ces petits.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.15","name":"Matthieu 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.13","name":"Matthieu 18:13","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.15","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:15","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Le pardon des offenses<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-20: cf. Ga 6:1. 1 Co 5. 2 Th 3:6, 14, 15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Si ton fr\u00e8re a p\u00e9ch\u00e9, va et reprends-le entre toi et lui seul. S\u2019il t\u2019\u00e9coute, tu as gagn\u00e9 ton fr\u00e8re.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.16","name":"Matthieu 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.14","name":"Matthieu 18:14","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.16","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:16","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais, s\u2019il ne t\u2019\u00e9coute pas, prends avec toi une ou deux personnes,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">afin que toute l\u2019affaire se r\u00e8gle sur la d\u00e9claration de deux ou de trois t\u00e9moins.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.17","name":"Matthieu 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.15","name":"Matthieu 18:15","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.17","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:17","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">S\u2019il refuse de les \u00e9couter,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">dis-le \u00e0 l\u2019\u00c9glise; et s\u2019il refuse aussi d\u2019\u00e9couter l\u2019\u00c9glise,<\/span><span class=\"wj\">qu\u2019il soit pour toi comme un pa\u00efen et un publicain.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.18","name":"Matthieu 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.16","name":"Matthieu 18:16","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.18","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:18","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous le dis en v\u00e9rit\u00e9, tout ce que vous lierez sur la terre sera li\u00e9 dans le ciel, et tout ce que vous d\u00e9lierez sur la terre sera d\u00e9li\u00e9 dans le ciel.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.19","name":"Matthieu 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.17","name":"Matthieu 18:17","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.19","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:19","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Je vous dis encore que, si deux d\u2019entre vous s\u2019accordent sur la terre pour demander une chose quelconque, elle leur sera accord\u00e9e par mon P\u00e8re qui est dans les cieux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.20","name":"Matthieu 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.18","name":"Matthieu 18:18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.20","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:20","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Car l\u00e0 o\u00f9 deux ou trois sont assembl\u00e9s en mon nom, je suis au milieu d\u2019eux.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.21","name":"Matthieu 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.19","name":"Matthieu 18:19","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.21","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:21","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.022,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Parabole du serviteur impitoyable<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 21-35: cf. Mt 6:12, 14, 15. \u00c9p 4:32; 5:1, 2. Ja 2:13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Alors Pierre s\u2019approcha de lui, et dit: Seigneur, combien de fois pardonnerai-je \u00e0 mon fr\u00e8re, lorsqu\u2019il p\u00e9chera contre moi? Sera-ce jusqu\u2019\u00e0 sept fois?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.22","name":"Matthieu 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.20","name":"Matthieu 18:20","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.22","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:22","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>J\u00e9sus lui dit: <span class=\"wj\">Je ne te dis pas jusqu\u2019\u00e0 sept fois, mais jusqu\u2019\u00e0<\/span> <span class=\"wj\">septante fois sept fois.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.23","name":"Matthieu 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.21","name":"Matthieu 18:21","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.23","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:23","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est pourquoi, le royaume des cieux est semblable \u00e0 un roi qui voulut faire rendre compte \u00e0 ses serviteurs.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.24","name":"Matthieu 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.22","name":"Matthieu 18:22","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.24","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:24","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Quand il se mit \u00e0 compter, on lui en amena un qui devait dix mille talents.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.25","name":"Matthieu 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.23","name":"Matthieu 18:23","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.25","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:25","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Comme il n\u2019avait pas de quoi payer, son ma\u00eetre ordonna qu\u2019il f\u00fbt vendu, lui, sa femme, ses enfants, et tout ce qu\u2019il avait, et que la dette f\u00fbt acquitt\u00e9e.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.26","name":"Matthieu 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.24","name":"Matthieu 18:24","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.26","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:26","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Le serviteur, se jetant \u00e0 terre, se prosterna devant lui, et dit: Seigneur, aie patience envers moi, et je te paierai tout.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.27","name":"Matthieu 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.25","name":"Matthieu 18:25","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.27","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:27","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">\u00c9mu de compassion, le ma\u00eetre de ce serviteur le laissa aller, et lui remit la dette.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.28","name":"Matthieu 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.26","name":"Matthieu 18:26","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.28","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:28","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Apr\u00e8s qu\u2019il fut sorti, ce serviteur rencontra un de ses compagnons qui lui devait cent deniers. Il le saisit et l\u2019\u00e9tranglait, en disant: Paie ce que tu me dois.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.29","name":"Matthieu 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.27","name":"Matthieu 18:27","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.29","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:29","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Son compagnon, se jetant \u00e0 terre, le suppliait, disant: Aie patience envers moi, et je te paierai.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.30","name":"Matthieu 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.28","name":"Matthieu 18:28","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.30","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:30","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Mais l\u2019autre ne voulut pas, et il alla le jeter en prison, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il e\u00fbt pay\u00e9 ce qu\u2019il devait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.31","name":"Matthieu 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.29","name":"Matthieu 18:29","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.31","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:31","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Ses compagnons, ayant vu ce qui \u00e9tait arriv\u00e9, furent profond\u00e9ment attrist\u00e9s, et ils all\u00e8rent raconter \u00e0 leur ma\u00eetre tout ce qui s\u2019\u00e9tait pass\u00e9.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.32","name":"Matthieu 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.30","name":"Matthieu 18:30","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.32","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:32","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Alors le ma\u00eetre fit appeler ce serviteur, et lui dit: M\u00e9chant serviteur, je t\u2019avais remis en entier ta dette, parce que tu m\u2019en avais suppli\u00e9;<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.33","name":"Matthieu 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.31","name":"Matthieu 18:31","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.33","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:33","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">ne devais-tu pas aussi avoir piti\u00e9 de ton compagnon, comme j\u2019ai eu piti\u00e9 de toi?<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.34","name":"Matthieu 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.32","name":"Matthieu 18:32","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.34","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:34","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.018.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">Et son ma\u00eetre, irrit\u00e9, le livra aux bourreaux, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce qu\u2019il e\u00fbt pay\u00e9 tout ce qu\u2019il devait.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.35","name":"Matthieu 18:35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.33","name":"Matthieu 18:33","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.35","label":"","reference":"Matthieu 18:35","prev_osis_id":"Matt.018.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Matt.019.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Matt.18.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup><span class=\"wj\">C\u2019est ainsi que mon P\u00e8re c\u00e9leste vous traitera, si chacun de vous ne pardonne \u00e0 son fr\u00e8re de tout son c\u0153ur.<\/span><\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Matt.18","name":"Matthieu 18","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.19.1","name":"Matthieu 19:1","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.19.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Matt.18.34","name":"Matthieu 18:34","id":"fra-LSG:Matt.18.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc696e124.37325632');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc696e124.37325632\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc696e124.37325632","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc696e124.37325632'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc696e124.37325632\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}